<h1>Host a Holiday Party</h1>
<p>String the lights and hang the garland, the holiday season has arrived! Planning to host a festive soiree? Invite your friends and neighbors to celebrate this season of giving while speeding a cure for Parkinson’s. Check out some of our tips and tricks below to get started.</p>
<h2 style="clear: both;">Instructions</h2>
<ol>
<li><span>1.</span>
<p><strong>Register:</strong> <a href="http://www2.michaeljfox.org/site/TR/Athletic/General?sid=1280&amp;type=fr_informational&amp;pg=informational&amp;fr_id=1890" style="color: orange;">Register online</a> as a Team Fox member and create a personalized fundraising page to share your event details and collect donations.  Once you register your event, we’ll send you a detailed step-by-step toolkit with an event checklist and helpful materials.</p>
</li>
<li><span>2.</span>
<p><strong>Start planning:</strong> From ornament decorating and cookie swaps to Secret Santa gifts and Christmas carol sing-a-longs, the sky is the limit! Whether you ask your guests to make a donation at the door or you include fun extras like a gift basket raffle to help raise funds, make sure you set a fundraising goal and identify a few ways to ways to reach it.</p>
</li>
<li><span>3.</span>
<p><strong>Outline the details:</strong> Pick a date and location — be sure to check your community’s calendar to avoid conflicting events. Planning to host a larger event? Consider asking a local restaurant, church or school to donate space for your use.</p>
</li>
<li><span>4.</span>
<p><strong>Recruit some help:</strong> Keep a list of the supplies you’ll need. Identify friends, businesses or restaurants to help get materials gathered or donated.</p>
</li>
<li><span>5.</span>
<p><strong>Get creative:</strong> Bring more fun to your event by including a holiday-themed costume, “ugly sweater” contest or a jingle competition.</p>
</li>
<li><span>6.</span>
<p><strong>Spread the word:</strong> Email invites to friends and neighbors or have teachers distribute flyers at school if you plan to host a larger event. Remember to include a link to your Team Fox page so that even if guests can’t attend or participate, they can still show support with a donation.</p>
</li>
<li><span>7.</span>
<p><strong>Inspire others:</strong> Held an awesome event? We want to hear all about it! Be sure to write up a quick recap and send us some photos to be entered to win a Team Fox Prize Pack! On social media? Like us on Facebook and share your updates on Twitter and Instagram using the hashtag: #TeamFoxHoliday</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p style="text-align: center;" class="pad20t"><a href="http://www2.michaeljfox.org/site/TR/Athletic/General?sid=1280&amp;type=fr_informational&amp;pg=informational&amp;fr_id=1890" class="mjffButton">     Get Started     </a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong> </strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Have a question? We’re here to help! Email us at <a href="mailto:teamfox@michaeljfox.org" style="color: orange;">teamfox@michaeljfox.org.</a></p>
